BPI Challenge 2012 event log.

DOI: 10.4121/uuid:3926db30-f712-4394-aebc-75976070e91f

This is an event log of a loan application process from a Dutch financial institute. The process is concerned with handling loan applications for private individuals. The data is enriched with decision and execution information added by a process mining tool.

Parameters:

  • root_folder (str, optional) – Path where the event log will be stored. Defaults to “data/”.

  • save_as_pandas (bool, optional) – Whether to save the event log as a pandas parquet file. Defaults to True.

  • train_set (bool, optional) – Whether to use the train set or the test set. If True, use the train set. If False, use the test set. Defaults to True.
